Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Welcome to this incredible opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine the possibilities on this prime lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}A rare permit-issued individual building lot awaits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Picture a stunning home on this 25 by 125 space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The city has already approved severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.26,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}With a city-assigned address, your dreams can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Think of all the designs you can create here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Whether you&apos;re a builder or an investor, this is gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Envision a vibrant community blossoming around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Just steps away from local amenities and parks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The potential here is truly limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Don&apos;t miss your chance to seize this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine your vision coming to life in this lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.89,0:00:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Thank you for exploring this unique chance with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}We can&apos;t wait to see what you create here.
